---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Avatar_250 from "../Avatar_250.webp";
import { SectionTitle } from "./UI";
---

<section id="about" class="w-full min-h-screen px-6 py-4 pt-14 bg-background">
    <SectionTitle
        title="About Me"
        color="primary"
        className="h-screen flex flex-col justify-center"
    >
        <div class="flex_center flex-col lg:flex-row w-full h-full py-10 gap-8">
            <Image
                src={Avatar_250}
                alt="About_Avatar"
                class="Fade_Up rounded-full scale-x-[-1] lg:mx-14"
                width={225}
                height={225}
                loading="lazy"
            />

            <div
                class="Fade_Up w-full md:w-[80%] lg:w-[60%] flex justify-center items-start flex-col gap-4 lg:border-l border-primary py-8 lg:pl-10"
            >
                <h2 class="Fade_Up text-[1.5em] font-bold">Hey there! 👋🏻</h2>
                <p class="Fade_Up text-justify">
                    I’m Adeoti Israel Adeola, a Software Developer and Information Systems student at the Federal University of Technology Akure (FUTA). I specialize in building functional, user-focused applications with clean design and efficient code.

                </p>
                <p class="Fade_Up text-justify">
                    My development journey has led me to work with technologies such as React Native, React.js, JavaScript, PHP, and MySQL, Python, Node js. I’m passionate about creating digital solutions that are both visually appealing and technically solid — bridging the gap between user experience and system logic.
                </p>
            
<p class="Fade_Up text-justify">
Beyond coding, I’m deeply interested in system design, innovation, and how technology can simplify complex problems. I take pride in writing code that’s reliable, maintainable, and built with purpose.

Let’s connect and bring ideas to life. 🚀
</p>
            </div>
        </div>

